{
  "stem": "21310.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, that was already during the bombardment and after my father had left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Up to that time, we were still in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I want to mention one thing quick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was some gas left in the pipes, high, because we were high up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we could still warm up some water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were hundreds of people in this apartment building in the lower and the entrance [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] doorways and in the halls on the bottom.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were all people, not so much refugees then, the people who-- whose houses already had burned down or had collapsed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were there, and many with small children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother was extremely busy making tea and warming some soup and, and always bringing food or bringing it down to these people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I never forget how people were blessing my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, they were all, you know, Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they would always say that God is going to be good to her because they were-- they were so grateful for what she was doing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and my mother always remembered that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes, you know, after the war and we all survived-- my, my parents survived too-- so that maybe, maybe that helped, all the blessings that she got from helping people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also, I remember one funny incident where we were sitting in this kind of shelter on some steps, and I was scratching.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had long braids, very dense hair, long braids, and I was scratching my head.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was sitting next to my mother, and she said, gee, you scratch as if you had lice.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, well, maybe I have lice.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
